welcome.full_message:
Welcome to Slack Coder!

Platform: {platform}
Agent: {agent}
User ID: {user_id}
Channel/Chat ID: {channel_id}

Commands:
@Slack Coder /start - Show this message
@Slack Coder /clear - Reset session and start fresh
@Slack Coder /cwd - Show current working directory
@Slack Coder /set_cwd <path> - Set working directory
@Slack Coder /settings - Personalization settings
@Slack Coder /stop - Interrupt {agent} execution

How it works:
- Send any message and it's immediately sent to {agent}
- Each chat maintains its own conversation context
- Use /clear to reset the conversation
